.Dt NCRASM 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ncrasm
.Nd assemble firmware for NCR 53C8XX SCSI I/O processors
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm ncrasm
.Op Fl cdlt 
.Op Fl p Ar prefix
.Ar input-file
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm Ncrasm
is used to assemble firmware for the NCR 53C8XX line of SCSI I/O
processors.
.Pp
The following options are available:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl c
Generate code segment.
.It Fl d
Output defines.
.It Fl l
Output listing.
.It Fl p Ar prefix
This is used to prefix a character string on all symbols generated.
.It Fl t
Output tags.
.El
.Pp
The
.Nm ncrasm
utility exits 0 on success, and >0 if an error occurs.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ncr 4
